				<title>Junior Staff Post</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-11573231/scp-4151#post-4242268</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2019 10:58:44 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Elogee FishTruck</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4037075</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The image used in this article is currently unsourced, and therefore may be a violation of the SCP wiki's license (CC BY-SA 3.0). If you can provide the source for the image, then I will determine whether it is cc-compliant or not. If it is, then the image will stay. If it isn't, the image will go.</p> <p>EDIT: The image has not been sourced by the author. However, I have investigated the source and I found it on <a href="https://www.alamy.com/stock-photo-ripe-wild-crab-apples-malus-sylvestris-in-the-new-forest-autumn-77057559.html?mid=41152&amp;siteID=MRu_ISar6sQ-XVTIm6EJ.4sRQfBJAEA0Pg&amp;utm_source=LS&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_content=US">Alamy</a>, which is non-compliant with the SCP wiki's license. Thus, the image has been removed.</p> <p>EDIT EDIT: The image has been replaced with a cc-compliant alternative, which can be found <a href="https://freerangestock.com/photos/77408/photo-details.html">here</a> (licensed under CC0).</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
