					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Quick thing: the phrasing &quot;Every human discovered has been matched to a pre-existing person in the Foundation's database.&quot; kinda implies that the orchard is duplicating the people, whereas the interview implies it's just teleporting the people [and i kinda feel like that paragraph should maybe be edited down a little; but it's probably fine as is].</p> <p>Otherwise this is pretty cool :3</p> 
				 	]]>
